杭州启动“复工专列”全国接人：免费乘坐，下车收礼包。
Hangzhou launched the "back to work train" national pick-up: free ride, get off the bus to receive gifts.
苏杰德。
Sujid.
中国新闻周刊                      。
China News Weekly.
